quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  11,108,"Si tawii non ko malaaЙ“e Й“en, ko ka nder Aljanna woni ko duumintee e mun fotde kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin no duumii, si wanaa si Joomi maa muuyii. (ЖҠum) ko dokkal ngal taЖҙondirtaa"
  11,109,"Wata a wonu e sikke e huunde ko Й“ee rewata. ЖҒe rewiraali si wanaa no baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e rewiray- noo ko adii. Menen non, Men hunniranay Й“e geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal ko aldah e Й—uytugol"
  11,110,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, luutondi- raa e mayre. Si wanaano konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. KamЙ“e kan hiЙ“e e sikke sikkitiiЙ—o e e mayre"
  11,111,Wonaali kala maЙ“Й“e si wanaa Joomi maa hunna- nay Й“e (njoЙ“di) kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet ko O humpitiiЙ—o ko Й“e gollata kon
  11,112,"Г‘iiЙ“ir [e focciingol ngol] wano yamiraЙ—aa non, e tuubuЙ“e wonnduЙ“e e maaЙ—a. Wata on bewu. Pellet ko O reenuЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  11,113,Wata on ooГұor e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en sakko Yiite ngen mema on. Alanah on gaanin Alla yiЙ—Й“e. Refti on walloytaake
  11,114,Г‘innu julde nden ka seraaji Й—iЙ—i Гұalorma e saa'iiji jemma. Pellet moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hino monta bonЙ—i Й—in. ЖҠum ko waaju wonannde Й“en waajitotooЙ“e
  11,115,MuГұГұo. Pellet Alla yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en
  11,116,"Ko haЙ—noo wona e gire adinooЙ“e on Й“en, joomiraa- Й“e kedde, Й“e no haЙ—a e bonnugol ka leydi! si seeЙ—aaЙ“e e Й“en Й“e Men daЙ—ndunoo e maЙ“Й“e. TooГұuЙ“e Й“en jokki e ko Й“e neeminaa e mun kon, Й“e laatii bomЙ“e"
  11,117,Joomi maa siforaali halkiroowo ca'e e hoore tooГұe tawa yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e
  11,118,"Sinno Joomi maa muuyiino, O waЙ—ayno yimЙ“e Й“en moftal gootal. ЖҒe seerataa ko Й“e luutondirooЙ“e"
  11,119,"si wanaa Й“en Й“e Joomi maa yurmaa. Ko sabu Й—um O tagiri Й“e. Konngol Joomi maa ngol jojjii wonnde: \"Pellet, Mi hebbiniray Jahannama jinna e yimЙ“e, Й“e denndaangal"
  11,120,"Kala e mu'un, MeЙ—en fillano maa kabaruuji NulaaЙ“e, ko Men tabintinra Й—um Й“ernnde maa ngon. Aranii ma e ngol (cortewol) goonga e waaju e janntoore wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  11,121,"Maakan Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inah: \"Gollee e nokku mo'on. Menen kadi, ko men gollooЙ“e"
  11,122,Habbitee kadi. Menen ko men habbitiiЙ“e
  11,123,"Ko Alla heeranii wirniiЙ—i kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, ko ka Makko fiyaaku no fow ruttetee. Awa rewu Mo, fawo-Й—aa e Makko. Joomi maa wonaali welsindiiЙ—o e kon ko golloton"
  12,1,"Alif, laam, raa. ЖҠen ko Aayeeje Deftere Й“anngunde nden"
  12,2,"Menen Men jippiniriinde janngeteende [e Й—emngal] Aarabu, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  12,3,"Menen MeЙ—en fillano maa ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e fillayee, e kon ko Men wahayini e maaЙ—a ndee Alqur'aanaare, hay si woniino ado mayre, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e welsindiiЙ“e Й“en"
  12,4,"Tuma nde Yuusufu maakannoo ben makko: \"Ko onon yo baaba'en, mi yi'ii [e koyЙ—ol] koode sappo e go'o, naange ngen kadi e lewru ndun; mi yi'ii Й—in no sujjana lam"
  12,5,"[Ben makko] maaki: \"Ko an yo Й“inngel am, wata a fillano musiЙ—Й“e maa Й“en koyЙ—ol maa ngol sakko Й“e fewjane feere; pellet seytaane ko gaГұoAade Й“annguЙ—o"
  12,6,"Ko wano nii Joomi maa suЙ“oray maa, O anndine firo koyЙ—i, O timmina neema Makko on e maaЙ—a e Й“eynguure Yaaquuba nden, wano O timminirnoo mo e baabiraaЙ“e maa Й“en Й—iЙ—o: Ibraahiima e ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"